REST: Rest to recover HP and SDC

Syntax: rest

DESCRIPTION:
  Your character sits down and rests. While resting, HP and SDC regenerate
  faster than normal. You cannot rest in combat.

  Use 'wake' to stand up and stop resting.

NOTES:
  - Resting does not work while fighting.
  - Moving or being attacked interrupts rest.
  - Your 'resting' status appears in your score.

SEE ALSO: wake, score
